019年5月主演的电视剧《麦香》播出。","name":"傅晶","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Fu Jing","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Fu Jing","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Фу Цзин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"傅晶，1977 年 3 月 19 日出生於湖北省武漢市，中國內地女演員，畢業於中央戲劇學院。\n\n2000 年參演個人首部電視劇《慾望阻擊》，從而進入演藝圈。2002 年因在都市情感劇《拿什麼拯救你，我的愛人》中飾演祝四萍一角而被觀眾所認識 。2008 年憑藉時裝懸疑劇《落地，請開手機》獲得更多關注。2011 年主演都市情感劇《大愛無聲》。2014 年主演時裝都市劇《團圓飯》。2016 年出演都市情感劇《安居》。2018 年拍攝都市情感劇《如果歲月可回頭》。2019 年 5 月主演的電視劇《麥香》播出。","name":"傅晶","primary":false}}]}},"person_1853386_translations":{"at":1773124737454,"data":{"id":1853386,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Allius Barnes","primary":true}}]}}}}